Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.60,0:22:02.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥　复杂的东西我怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.10,0:22:03.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊
